Package org.accada.ale.server

Class Summary
ALE This class represents the application level events interface.
EventCycle This class represents an event cycle.
Pattern This class represents an tag, filter or group pattern.
PatternDataField This clas represents a data field of a tag, filter or group pattern.
Report This class represents a report.
ReportsGenerator This class generates ec reports.
Subscriber This class represents a subscriber of an ec specification.
Tag represents a tag that has been read on one of the readers in the Logical Reader API.
 

Enum Summary
PatternType This enumeration defines the possible pattern types.
PatternUsage This enumeration contains the possible usages of a pattern.
ReportsGeneratorState This enumeration contains all reports generator states.
